Events
onclick --> the normal button is clicked
<form onclick="abc()"><button>Click</button></form>

onsubmit --> the submit buttion clicked
<form onsubmit="abc()"><button type=submit>Click</button></form>

onfocus --> when the input box is clicked
<input onfocus="abc()" />

onblur --> when the input is taken back from place
<input onblur="abc()" />

onkeyup --> when the key is pressed
onchange --> when there is a change in input
onmouseover --> when the mouse is hovered over it

